            <V n="text" t="single">
              <T n="single">0x7566804<!--Today is a <b>Waning Gibbous Moon</b>, so here's what I can share with you, Kiddo:\n\nSpecters... And I don't mean Olive and company with all of her <i>drama</i>. I mean the little floaty fellas you see at Crow's Crossing or when you ring the Mourningvale Bell Tower bells. Believe it or not, they were once living Sims, but their sense of self has been long lost to them, either willingly or forgotten. The whole thing is, as youths would put it, a <i>brain rotten</i> situation if you ask me. Still, I understand why Sims around these parts think Specters have <i>The Rizz</i>. They radiate pure positivity, and that's a-okay in my book.--></T>
